{"tid":573996,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"別一個人吃飯了！日研究：孤單進食容易死掉、憂鬱","createTime":"2018-02-27T03:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:09:11.000Z","uid":1121,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1300d0f41d05cf288af8a54b7f78f92d8662c556","tid":573996,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"平時下班時間不固定，習慣一個人吃飯嗎？未來你可能需要個「飯友」了！因為日本一項研究指出，一個人吃飯的死亡風險，是跟別人一起吃飯的1.5倍，憂鬱症發病機率更是2.7倍！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3127/d3127276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3127%2Fd3127276.jpg&h=c741937f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲跟別人同居的話，就一起吃飯吧！（圖／<a href=\"http://翻攝自www.jages.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E6%94%9D%E8%87%AAwww.jages.net&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=ebc4fe35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻攝自www.jages.net</a>）"},{"pid":"23b90e2b2a9f8e28d03496597806289ad3fd6375","tid":573996,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"日本東京大學營養學研究員谷友香子， 於2014年至2016年間進行近3年長的研究，針對約7萬名65歲以上的老年人做飲食調查。發現高齡男子若跟別人同住，卻一個人吃飯，死亡風險相較跟別人同住，一起吃飯高出47%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3127/d3127271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3127%2Fd3127271.jpg&h=cd849a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲一個人居住、一個人吃飯，憂鬱症發病機率也都高出許多。（圖／<a href=\"http://翻攝自www.jages.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E6%94%9D%E8%87%AAwww.jages.net&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=ebc4fe35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻攝自www.jages.net</a>）<br />\n<br />\n她也於 2013年所做相關研究，發現高齡男子若一個人居住，也一個人吃飯，相較一個人居住、跟別人一起吃飯，前者患有憂鬱症的機率更是後者2.7倍。"},{"pid":"113b6b186006b3de7cca2b5992e1b216dd84924c","tid":573996,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"為什麼一個人吃飯會有如此風險？研究指出，因為孤單進食時，會覺得吃飯少了樂趣，便會加速吃完， 咀嚼次數變少、減少唾液分泌，可能造成腸胃道負擔，有「快樂賀爾蒙」的血清素也會因此減少分泌。<br />\n<br />\n一個人吃飯，還有可能會「隨便吃」，研究發現超過20%的獨居老人會習慣「一天2餐」、容易忽視飲食營養及均衡，都是高齡化社會的隱憂。高達70%的獨居老人礙於現實考量，只能一個人吃飯，但內心其實 「很想跟別人一起吃飯」。<br />\n<br />\n日本媒體建議，若是一個人居住，不妨常跟朋友一起用餐，或是到熟悉的店面裡，跟老闆、熟客聊天。另外也建議在陽光下吃飯，保持開朗心情、微笑，才能夠分泌血清素，趕走吃飯時的「寂寞感」。"},{"pid":"4207cb339a38b3875ac76e6e594753b7bad5a6c9","tid":573996,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fashion.ettoday.net/news/1117797?from=fb_et_beauty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffashion.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1117797%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_beauty&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=aaee8311\" target=\"_blank\">https://fashion.ettoday.net/news/1117797?from=fb_et_beauty</a>"},{"pid":"fbd31527325c80867aec676a4b817d41e247842b","tid":573996,"uid":171594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"咁自己一個打J會唔會早死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76aa09affd48634b826ed02780c36a905951e09c","tid":573996,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa46a8a39bc29f013e1693e2d5d7a39d85390bd9","tid":573996,"uid":18568,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"你估我想咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"1d484ab83bad7b855fda27aa3d19999d70d0d5e1","tid":573996,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f0bff362baf2326e2c9eae6ba8b7cefba5b3c0","tid":573996,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa46a8a39bc29f013e1693e2d5d7a39d85390bd9","tid":573996,"uid":18568,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime